supplier.company_profile_text: Suite Bar is New Zealand's most awarded cocktail bar. It showcases the widest range of New Zealand craft beers, an award winning local wine list, a seasonal food menu and has the best range of spirits in the country. For your best New Zealand experience, look no further.

The Conservatory - it's about living: The Conservatory is literally full of life, it's New Zealand's first living bar. That place you can go for breakfast, lunch or grab an 18 inch pizza, and ice cold pint or indulge in some boutique wines or amazing cocktails. That place that the outside is as comfortable as the inside. That place with an open fire. That place by the sea.

supplier.company_profile_text: The Paddington is one of the top spots in central Auckland to unwind after work or take in a sports event, situated only 5 minutes from Vector Arena, it's also the perfect spot for pre-concert dinner & drinks. Full HDMI facilites, The Paddington is regarded as a sporting mecca with the best atmosphere outside of Eden Park.

If you love Thai food in a warm cosy atmosphere with great service, you will not be disappointed with Auckland's latest taste sensation. The restaurant offers great wines, cocktails and beers. Please ensure your seats by booking early. Innovative authentic Thai cuisine.

supplier.company_profile_text: The Ponsonby BBC is located in the old post office, Ponsonby's best know heritage landmark building. It is a French cosmopolitan style Belgian beer cafe, just like the typical great brasseries found on the Grand Place in Brussels. The Ponsonby BBC specializes in contemporary Belgian cusine using the best French produce New Zealand has to offer. Combined with the largest Belgian speciality beer list in the Southern Hemisphere, the Ponsonby BBC is just an awesome experience you don't want to miss, be it for drinks, a nice meal, function or special occasion!

Delicious kiwi fare. Restored native timerb interior, big screen TVs, open fires and a covered courtyard deck with louvered roof means year-long alfresco socialising.

supplier.company_profile_text: Wonderful venue for wedding receptions and special celebrations, plus conference facilities. We can accomodate smaller intimate groups of 20 up to 150. Beautiful panoramic views over the 18th green. Cafe open 7 days a week (licensed). Everyone welcome.

Adriana's Caffe & Ristorante - Hamilton's first authentic Italian restaurant and more than 20 years later, still renowned for its antipasti, pasta, pesce, chicken, succulent steaks and decadent dolce. Fully Licensed, open 6pm daily. 6 Alma Street adjacent to Novotel, Ibis & Casino. (Also see our Garden Terrace listing for all-day alfresco dining).

Breakers is a great place to relax and unwind with family or friends. Fully licensed with a wide menu selection, we source the best ingredients which we know you will appreciate. We're also the perfect venue for larger families and group bookings. There's a dedicated kids menu and kids area too. Open 7 days.

Set in the heart of the south end of Victoria Street, Easy Tiger is Hamilton's premium cocktail bar. Enjoy exquisite cocktails mixed by our skilled bartenders while you sample a light meal from our Asian - inspired menu. The contemporary East-meets-West decor combines comfort with style to produce a truly impressive finish.

The Abbey Belgian Beer Cafe is one of Hamilton's most unique hospitality experiences. With an authentic Belgian fit-out, over 30 Belgian beers and a traditional Belgian menu combining French finesse and German generosity. The Abbey is a taste of Belgium right here in the Waikato.

Furnace finds the perfect harmony between casual dining and bar culture. Friendly staff, a well-appointed interior and welcoming fires create a warm ambiance. Furnace has something for everyone, from renowned pizzas and pastas to more refined main meals complemented by a comprehensive selection of quality wine and beers.

The Bank is one of Hamilton's most iconic bars and has been a popular destination since it opened in 1994. The versatile gasto bar offers a comprehensive range of quality wines and draught beer as well as contemporary dining featuring a steak menu fit for any steak lover.
